  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face monsters in a 2D pixel art bullet hell to prove your worth and join Captain Cesar's pirate crew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start your challenge by choosing weapons with different abilities and stats.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/8b07aa688871ea705b361840195cdb3d.poster.avif?t=1740770160\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/8b07aa688871ea705b361840195cdb3d.webm?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/8b07aa688871ea705b361840195cdb3d.mp4?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight hordes of monsters with varying patterns and difficulties.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/b6236a20be61cff220af51b29f745903.poster.avif?t=1740770160\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/b6236a20be61cff220af51b29f745903.webm?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/b6236a20be61cff220af51b29f745903.mp4?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect coins to purchase upgrades or make your journey easier by buying skill drops.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/84a8b76b2ce61566b6037d9cdcb1c622.poster.avif?t=1740770160\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/84a8b76b2ce61566b6037d9cdcb1c622.webm?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/84a8b76b2ce61566b6037d9cdcb1c622.mp4?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/14ae6d262bbd5a89b495fd3386ea3961.poster.avif?t=1740770160\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/14ae6d262bbd5a89b495fd3386ea3961.webm?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/14ae6d262bbd5a89b495fd3386ea3961.mp4?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't be fooled by the initial ease; the monsters will pile up, and you'll need to be ready for the challenge.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/82382c4439c2b382e5654138feb6f8bf.poster.avif?t=1740770160\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/82382c4439c2b382e5654138feb6f8bf.webm?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265380/extras/82382c4439c2b382e5654138feb6f8bf.mp4?t=1740770160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve your highest score and compete with your friends on the leaderboard to see who is the most worthy to set sail on the seven seas with Cesar's crew!</p>",
